Number of partitions for k-fold test

Comment.Text: This combines the adaptive learning scenario with the subject independent scenario. The first ten symbols will be classified by the mixture of experts (the left branch after the stream switch). After the 10 symbols, an inital spatial filter and classifier is computed based on its predictions. This classifier is then loaded by the adaptive p300 classifier box and further adapted based on the predictions (the right branch under the stream swicth)
